'''Eletrotex''', also known as '''electrotex''', was a type of [[nanoweave]] [[Armor/Legends|armor]]. It was gray, opalescent, and expensive, being renowned more for its appearance than for its armor abilities. Around [[41 ABY]] it was also part of best available [[Environment suit/Legends|enviro-suits]].

